OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784294320
OL,3,CTractor driver arrested after
OL,4,Ccollision which injured five
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FA tractor driver has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving after a
OL,9,Fcollision which injured five
OL,10,Ffirefighters.
OL,12,FThe incident happened on Sark on the
OL,13,Fafternoon of Friday 12 July while the
OL,14,Fcrew, who had been brought over from
OL,15,FGuernsey, were travelling to tackle a
OL,16,Fmajor wildfire.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
