PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784294320
OL,3,CTractor driver arrested after
OL,4,Ccollision which injured five
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FThey suffered non-life threatening
OL,8,Finjuries and were transferred to
OL,9,FGuernsey's Princess Elizabeth Hospital
OL,10,Ffor treatment, where they were all
OL,11,Fdischarged within 24 hours.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Guernsey Police has
OL,14,Fconfirmed that it arrested the tractor
OL,15,Fdriver on the day of the collision -
OL,16,Fhaving been invited over by the Sark
OL,17,FConstable.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
