OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1784294320
OL,3,CTractor driver arrested after
OL,4,Ccollision which injured five
OL,5,Cfirefighters
OL,7,FThey add: "At the time, police ensured
OL,8,Fthat the priority of all emergency
OL,9,Fservices in Sark remained on tackling
OL,10,Fthe fire, however enquiries are now
OL,11,Fongoing and the suspect is on police
OL,12,Fbail."
